FRESNO, Calif. (KMPH) — UPDATE:
Fresno police say just before 7:00 a.m., a man in his 50s was walking his bike along the train tracks near Church and East.The man waited for a freight train to pass but stepped out in front of an oncoming Amtrak traveling the other way.Police believe it was just an accident.
